    <h1>Newsletter</h1>
    <p class="description">A regularly scheduled email delivering value to subscribers — news, education, product updates, or curated resources. Unlike social media reach, your subscriber list belongs to you, not to an algorithm. Average email ROI: <strong>$36 per $1 spent</strong>.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
